    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1885-05-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1885-05-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="111" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d111">
                <head>No. 107.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Beach</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-05-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 15,
                            1885</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Flores has telegraphed permission for Santos to come to United States. You
                        will assist his departure.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>BAYARD.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
